2026-02-07T20:19:52.234+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-5] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
        AND MSG.CN_MSG_NO < ?  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30 
Hibernate:

        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM

2026-02-07T20:19:53.485+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-3] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
        AND MSG.CN_MSG_NO < ?  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

2026-02-07T20:20:03.958+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-1] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        CNR.CN_NO        AS ROOM_NO,
        -- 클랜채팅방번호
         CNR.CN_ROOM_NM   AS ROOM_NM,
        -- 클랜채팅방이름
         (           SELECT
            MSG.MSG           
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.CN_NO = CNR.CN_NO             
            AND MSG.SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'           
        ORDER BY
            MSG.SND_DTIME DESC           
        LIMIT
            1         ) AS NEW_MSG,
        -- 신규메시지
         (           SELECT
            COUNT(1)           
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.CN_NO = CNR.CN_NO             
            AND MSG.SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                   AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'             
            AND NOT EXISTS (                 SELECT
                1                 FROM CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ MSR                 
            WHERE
                MSR.CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO                   
                AND MSR.READ_USER_ID = ?             )         ) AS NEW_MSG_READ_CNT,
        -- 채팅읽지않은건수
         'CLAN' AS ROOM_TYPE,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH     
    FROM
        CN_USER CNU     
    INNER JOIN
        CN_GROUP CNG 
            ON CNG.CN_NO = CNU.CN_NO     
    INNER JOIN
        CN_CHAT_ROOM CNR 
            ON CNR.CN_NO = CNU.CN_NO     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = CNG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        CNU.CN_USER_ID = ?         
        AND CNU.CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A'         
        AND CNU.CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN'         
        AND CNG.CN_STAT_CD = 'A'         
        AND CNG.CN_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN'      
    UNION
    ALL      SELECT
        CNR.BN_NO        AS ROOM_NO,
        -- 합주채팅방번호
         CNR.BN_ROOM_NM   AS ROOM_NM,
        -- 합주채팅방이름
         (           SELECT
            MSG.BN_CHAT_MSG           
        FROM
            BN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.BN_NO = CNR.BN_NO             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'           
        ORDER BY
            MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME DESC           
        LIMIT
            1         ) AS NEW_MSG,
        -- 신규메시지
         (           SELECT
            COUNT(1)           
        FROM
            BN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.BN_NO = CNR.BN_NO             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'             
            AND NOT EXISTS (                 SELECT
                1                 FROM BN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ MSR                 
            WHERE
                MSR.BN_CHAT_MSG_NO = MSG.BN_CHAT_MSG_NO                   
                AND MSR.BN_CHAT_READ_USER_ID = ?             )         ) AS NEW_MSG_READ_CNT,
        -- 채팅읽지않은건수
         'BAND' AS ROOM_TYPE,
        NULL AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH     
    FROM
        BN_USER BNU     
    INNER JOIN
        BN_GROUP BNG 
            ON BNG.BN_NO = BNU.BN_NO     
    INNER JOIN
        BN_CHAT_ROOM CNR 
            ON CNR.BN_NO = BNU.BN_NO     
    WHERE
        BNU.BN_USER_ID = ?         
        AND BNU.BN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A'         
        AND BNG.BN_STAT_CD = 'A'

        WHERE
            MSG.BN_NO = CNR.BN_NO             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'           
        ORDER BY
            MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME DESC           
        LIMIT
            1         ) AS NEW_MSG,
        -- 신규메시지
         (           SELECT
            COUNT(1)           
        FROM
            BN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.BN_NO = CNR.BN_NO             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'             
            AND NOT EXISTS (                 SELECT
                1                 FROM BN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ MSR                 
            WHERE
                MSR.BN_CHAT_MSG_NO = MSG.BN_CHAT_MSG_NO                   
                AND MSR.BN_CHAT_READ_USER_ID = ?             )         ) AS NEW_MSG_READ_CNT,
        -- 채팅읽지않은건수
         'BAND' AS ROOM_TYPE,
        NULL AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH     
    FROM
        BN_USER BNU     
    INNER JOIN
        BN_GROUP BNG 
            ON BNG.BN_NO = BNU.BN_NO     
    INNER JOIN
        BN_CHAT_ROOM CNR 
            ON CNR.BN_NO = BNU.BN_NO     
    WHERE
        BNU.BN_USER_ID = ?         
        AND BNU.BN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A'         
        AND BNG.BN_STAT_CD = 'A' 
Hibernate: 
    SELECT
        CNR.CN_NO        AS ROOM_NO,
        -- 클랜채팅방번호
         CNR.CN_ROOM_NM   AS ROOM_NM,
        -- 클랜채팅방이름
         (           SELECT
            MSG.MSG           
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.CN_NO = CNR.CN_NO             
            AND MSG.SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'           
        ORDER BY
            MSG.SND_DTIME DESC           
        LIMIT
            1         ) AS NEW_MSG,
        -- 신규메시지
         (           SELECT
            COUNT(1)           
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.CN_NO = CNR.CN_NO             
            AND MSG.SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                   AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'             
            AND NOT EXISTS (                 SELECT
                1                 FROM CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ MSR                 
            WHERE
                MSR.CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO                   
                AND MSR.READ_USER_ID = ?             )         ) AS NEW_MSG_READ_CNT,
        -- 채팅읽지않은건수
         'CLAN' AS ROOM_TYPE,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH     
    FROM
        CN_USER CNU     
    INNER JOIN
        CN_GROUP CNG 
            ON CNG.CN_NO = CNU.CN_NO     
    INNER JOIN
        CN_CHAT_ROOM CNR 
            ON CNR.CN_NO = CNU.CN_NO     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = CNG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        CNU.CN_USER_ID = ?         
        AND CNU.CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A'         
        AND CNU.CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN'         
        AND CNG.CN_STAT_CD = 'A'         
        AND CNG.CN_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN'      
    UNION
    ALL      SELECT
        CNR.BN_NO        AS ROOM_NO,
        -- 합주채팅방번호
         CNR.BN_ROOM_NM   AS ROOM_NM,
        -- 합주채팅방이름
         (           SELECT
            MSG.BN_CHAT_MSG           
        FROM
            BN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.BN_NO = CNR.BN_NO             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'           
        ORDER BY
            MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME DESC           
        LIMIT
            1         ) AS NEW_MSG,
        -- 신규메시지
         (           SELECT
            COUNT(1)           
        FROM
            BN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.BN_NO = CNR.BN_NO             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'             
            AND NOT EXISTS (                 SELECT
                1                 FROM BN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ MSR                 
            WHERE
                MSR.BN_CHAT_MSG_NO = MSG.BN_CHAT_MSG_NO                   
                AND MSR.BN_CHAT_READ_USER_ID = ?             )         ) AS NEW_MSG_READ_CNT,
        -- 채팅읽지않은건수
         'BAND' AS ROOM_TYPE,
        NULL AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH     
    FROM
        BN_USER BNU     
    INNER JOIN
        BN_GROUP BNG 
            ON BNG.BN_NO = BNU.BN_NO     
    INNER JOIN
        BN_CHAT_ROOM CNR 
            ON CNR.BN_NO = BNU.BN_NO     
    WHERE
        BNU.BN_USER_ID = ?         
        AND BNU.BN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A'         
        AND BNG.BN_STAT_CD = 'A' 
2026-02-07T20:20:05.301+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-6] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

2026-02-07T20:20:05.318+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-9] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

        MSG.SND_DTIME,

            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID

            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO

            COUNT(1) 
        FROM

        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE

        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG

        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID

    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

2026-02-07T20:22:44.739+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-3] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

2026-02-07T20:22:48.680+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-4] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
        AND MSG.CN_MSG_NO < ?  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30 
Hibernate: 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,

        MSG.SND_DTIME,

            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A'

            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ

            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,

        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM

        MM_USER USR

2026-02-07T20:22:49.863+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-6] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
        AND MSG.CN_MSG_NO < ?  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30 
Hibernate:

        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,

    SELECT
        CNR.CN_NO        AS ROOM_NO,
        -- 클랜채팅방번호
         CNR.CN_ROOM_NM   AS ROOM_NM,
        -- 클랜채팅방이름
         (           SELECT
            MSG.MSG           
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.CN_NO = CNR.CN_NO             
            AND MSG.SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'           
        ORDER BY
            MSG.SND_DTIME DESC           
        LIMIT
            1         ) AS NEW_MSG,
        -- 신규메시지
         (           SELECT
            COUNT(1)           
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.CN_NO = CNR.CN_NO             
            AND MSG.SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                   AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'             
            AND NOT EXISTS (                 SELECT
                1                 FROM CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ MSR                 
            WHERE
                MSR.CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO                   
                AND MSR.READ_USER_ID = ?             )         ) AS NEW_MSG_READ_CNT,
        -- 채팅읽지않은건수
         'CLAN' AS ROOM_TYPE,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH     
    FROM
        CN_USER CNU     
    INNER JOIN
        CN_GROUP CNG 
            ON CNG.CN_NO = CNU.CN_NO     
    INNER JOIN
        CN_CHAT_ROOM CNR 
            ON CNR.CN_NO = CNU.CN_NO     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = CNG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        CNU.CN_USER_ID = ?         
        AND CNU.CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A'         
        AND CNU.CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN'         
        AND CNG.CN_STAT_CD = 'A'         
        AND CNG.CN_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN'      
    UNION
    ALL      SELECT
        CNR.BN_NO        AS ROOM_NO,
        -- 합주채팅방번호
         CNR.BN_ROOM_NM   AS ROOM_NM,

            MSG.BN_CHAT_MSG           
        FROM
            BN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE

        ORDER BY
            MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME DESC           
        LIMIT
            1         ) AS NEW_MSG,
        -- 신규메시지
         (           SELECT
            COUNT(1)           
        FROM
            BN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.BN_NO = CNR.BN_NO             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'             
            AND NOT EXISTS (                 SELECT

            WHERE
                MSR.BN_CHAT_MSG_NO = MSG.BN_CHAT_MSG_NO                   
                AND MSR.BN_CHAT_READ_USER_ID = ?             )         ) AS NEW_MSG_READ_CNT,
        -- 채팅읽지않은건수
         'BAND' AS ROOM_TYPE,
        NULL AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH

2026-02-07T20:22:58.527+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-8] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

2026-02-07T20:22:58.553+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [io-8083-exec-10] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30 
Hibernate: 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

2026-02-07T20:23:05.561+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-5] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
        AND MSG.CN_MSG_NO < ?  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

2026-02-07T20:23:08.161+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-7] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
        AND MSG.CN_MSG_NO < ?  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

2026-02-07T20:23:10.408+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-3] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        CNR.CN_NO        AS ROOM_NO,
        -- 클랜채팅방번호
         CNR.CN_ROOM_NM   AS ROOM_NM,
        -- 클랜채팅방이름
         (           SELECT
            MSG.MSG           
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.CN_NO = CNR.CN_NO             
            AND MSG.SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'           
        ORDER BY
            MSG.SND_DTIME DESC           
        LIMIT
            1         ) AS NEW_MSG,
        -- 신규메시지
         (           SELECT
            COUNT(1)           
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.CN_NO = CNR.CN_NO             
            AND MSG.SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                   AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'             
            AND NOT EXISTS (                 SELECT
                1                 FROM CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ MSR                 
            WHERE
                MSR.CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO                   
                AND MSR.READ_USER_ID = ?             )         ) AS NEW_MSG_READ_CNT,
        -- 채팅읽지않은건수
         'CLAN' AS ROOM_TYPE,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH     
    FROM
        CN_USER CNU     
    INNER JOIN
        CN_GROUP CNG 
            ON CNG.CN_NO = CNU.CN_NO     
    INNER JOIN
        CN_CHAT_ROOM CNR 
            ON CNR.CN_NO = CNU.CN_NO     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = CNG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        CNU.CN_USER_ID = ?         
        AND CNU.CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A'         
        AND CNU.CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN'         
        AND CNG.CN_STAT_CD = 'A'         
        AND CNG.CN_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN'      
    UNION
    ALL      SELECT
        CNR.BN_NO        AS ROOM_NO,
        -- 합주채팅방번호
         CNR.BN_ROOM_NM   AS ROOM_NM,
        -- 합주채팅방이름
         (           SELECT
            MSG.BN_CHAT_MSG           
        FROM
            BN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.BN_NO = CNR.BN_NO             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'           
        ORDER BY
            MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME DESC           
        LIMIT
            1         ) AS NEW_MSG,
        -- 신규메시지
         (           SELECT
            COUNT(1)           
        FROM
            BN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.BN_NO = CNR.BN_NO             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'             
            AND NOT EXISTS (                 SELECT
                1                 FROM BN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ MSR                 
            WHERE
                MSR.BN_CHAT_MSG_NO = MSG.BN_CHAT_MSG_NO                   
                AND MSR.BN_CHAT_READ_USER_ID = ?             )         ) AS NEW_MSG_READ_CNT,
        -- 채팅읽지않은건수
         'BAND' AS ROOM_TYPE,
        NULL AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH     
    FROM
        BN_USER BNU     
    INNER JOIN
        BN_GROUP BNG 
            ON BNG.BN_NO = BNU.BN_NO     
    INNER JOIN
        BN_CHAT_ROOM CNR 
            ON CNR.BN_NO = BNU.BN_NO     
    WHERE
        BNU.BN_USER_ID = ?         
        AND BNU.BN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A'         
        AND BNG.BN_STAT_CD = 'A'

2026-02-07T20:23:11.393+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-4] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

2026-02-07T20:23:11.409+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-6] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30 
Hibernate: 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

2026-02-07T20:25:32.731+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-5] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

2026-02-07T20:25:32.757+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-3] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

            COUNT(1) 
        FROM

        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO

            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ

        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID

            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO

2026-02-07T20:26:19.686+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-9] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

2026-02-07T20:26:24.506+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-8] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        CNR.CN_NO        AS ROOM_NO,
        -- 클랜채팅방번호
         CNR.CN_ROOM_NM   AS ROOM_NM,
        -- 클랜채팅방이름
         (           SELECT
            MSG.MSG           
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.CN_NO = CNR.CN_NO             
            AND MSG.SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'           
        ORDER BY
            MSG.SND_DTIME DESC           
        LIMIT
            1         ) AS NEW_MSG,
        -- 신규메시지
         (           SELECT
            COUNT(1)           
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.CN_NO = CNR.CN_NO             
            AND MSG.SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                   AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'             
            AND NOT EXISTS (                 SELECT
                1                 FROM CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ MSR                 
            WHERE
                MSR.CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO                   
                AND MSR.READ_USER_ID = ?             )         ) AS NEW_MSG_READ_CNT,
        -- 채팅읽지않은건수
         'CLAN' AS ROOM_TYPE,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH     
    FROM
        CN_USER CNU     
    INNER JOIN
        CN_GROUP CNG 
            ON CNG.CN_NO = CNU.CN_NO     
    INNER JOIN
        CN_CHAT_ROOM CNR 
            ON CNR.CN_NO = CNU.CN_NO     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = CNG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        CNU.CN_USER_ID = ?         
        AND CNU.CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A'         
        AND CNU.CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN'         
        AND CNG.CN_STAT_CD = 'A'         
        AND CNG.CN_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN'      
    UNION
    ALL      SELECT
        CNR.BN_NO        AS ROOM_NO,
        -- 합주채팅방번호
         CNR.BN_ROOM_NM   AS ROOM_NM,
        -- 합주채팅방이름
         (           SELECT
            MSG.BN_CHAT_MSG           
        FROM
            BN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.BN_NO = CNR.BN_NO             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'           
        ORDER BY
            MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME DESC           
        LIMIT
            1         ) AS NEW_MSG,
        -- 신규메시지
         (           SELECT
            COUNT(1)           
        FROM
            BN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.BN_NO = CNR.BN_NO             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'             
            AND NOT EXISTS (                 SELECT
                1                 FROM BN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ MSR                 
            WHERE
                MSR.BN_CHAT_MSG_NO = MSG.BN_CHAT_MSG_NO                   
                AND MSR.BN_CHAT_READ_USER_ID = ?             )         ) AS NEW_MSG_READ_CNT,
        -- 채팅읽지않은건수
         'BAND' AS ROOM_TYPE,
        NULL AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH     
    FROM
        BN_USER BNU     
    INNER JOIN
        BN_GROUP BNG 
            ON BNG.BN_NO = BNU.BN_NO     
    INNER JOIN
        BN_CHAT_ROOM CNR 
            ON CNR.BN_NO = BNU.BN_NO     
    WHERE
        BNU.BN_USER_ID = ?         
        AND BNU.BN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A'         
        AND BNG.BN_STAT_CD = 'A' 
Hibernate: 
    SELECT
        CNR.CN_NO        AS ROOM_NO,
        -- 클랜채팅방번호
         CNR.CN_ROOM_NM   AS ROOM_NM,
        -- 클랜채팅방이름
         (           SELECT
            MSG.MSG           
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.CN_NO = CNR.CN_NO             
            AND MSG.SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'           
        ORDER BY
            MSG.SND_DTIME DESC           
        LIMIT
            1         ) AS NEW_MSG,
        -- 신규메시지
         (           SELECT
            COUNT(1)           
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.CN_NO = CNR.CN_NO             
            AND MSG.SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                   AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'             
            AND NOT EXISTS (                 SELECT
                1                 FROM CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ MSR                 
            WHERE
                MSR.CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO                   
                AND MSR.READ_USER_ID = ?             )         ) AS NEW_MSG_READ_CNT,
        -- 채팅읽지않은건수
         'CLAN' AS ROOM_TYPE,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH     
    FROM
        CN_USER CNU     
    INNER JOIN
        CN_GROUP CNG 
            ON CNG.CN_NO = CNU.CN_NO     
    INNER JOIN
        CN_CHAT_ROOM CNR 
            ON CNR.CN_NO = CNU.CN_NO     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = CNG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        CNU.CN_USER_ID = ?         
        AND CNU.CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A'         
        AND CNU.CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN'         
        AND CNG.CN_STAT_CD = 'A'         
        AND CNG.CN_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN'      
    UNION
    ALL      SELECT
        CNR.BN_NO        AS ROOM_NO,
        -- 합주채팅방번호
         CNR.BN_ROOM_NM   AS ROOM_NM,
        -- 합주채팅방이름
         (           SELECT
            MSG.BN_CHAT_MSG           
        FROM
            BN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.BN_NO = CNR.BN_NO             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'           
        ORDER BY
            MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME DESC           
        LIMIT
            1         ) AS NEW_MSG,
        -- 신규메시지
         (           SELECT
            COUNT(1)           
        FROM
            BN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.BN_NO = CNR.BN_NO             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'             
            AND NOT EXISTS (                 SELECT
                1                 FROM BN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ MSR                 
            WHERE
                MSR.BN_CHAT_MSG_NO = MSG.BN_CHAT_MSG_NO                   
                AND MSR.BN_CHAT_READ_USER_ID = ?             )         ) AS NEW_MSG_READ_CNT,
        -- 채팅읽지않은건수
         'BAND' AS ROOM_TYPE,
        NULL AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH     
    FROM
        BN_USER BNU     
    INNER JOIN
        BN_GROUP BNG 
            ON BNG.BN_NO = BNU.BN_NO     
    INNER JOIN
        BN_CHAT_ROOM CNR 
            ON CNR.BN_NO = BNU.BN_NO     
    WHERE
        BNU.BN_USER_ID = ?         
        AND BNU.BN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A'         
        AND BNG.BN_STAT_CD = 'A'

    select
        cg1_0.cn_no,
        cg1_0.cn_nm,
        cg1_0.cn_desc,
        cg1_0.cn_url,
        (select
            count(*) 
        from
            cn_user cu1_0 
        where
            cu1_0.cn_no=cg1_0.cn_no 
            and cu1_0.cn_user_stat_cd='A' 
            and cu1_0.cn_user_appr_stat_cd='CN'),
        ca1_0.file_path,
        (select
            count(ccm1_0.cn_msg_no) 
        from
            cn_chat_message ccm1_0 
        where
            ccm1_0.cn_no=cg1_0.cn_no 
            and ccm1_0.snd_user_id<>? 
            and not exists(select
                ccmr1_0.cn_msg_no, ccmr1_0.read_user_id from cn_chat_message_read ccmr1_0 
            where
                ccmr1_0.cn_msg_no=ccm1_0.cn_msg_no 
                and ccmr1_0.read_user_id=?)) 
    from
        cn_group cg1_0 
    left join
        cm_attachment ca1_0 
            on cg1_0.attach_no=ca1_0.attach_no 
    where
        cg1_0.cn_no=?
2026-02-07T20:26:25.150+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-3] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        K.CN_NO AS "cnNo",
        K.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO AS "cnBoardTypeNo",
        B.CN_BOARD_NO AS "cnBoardNo",
        B.TITLE AS "title",
        B.INS_DTIME AS "regDate",
        (SELECT
            U.USER_NICK_NM 
        FROM
            MM_USER U 
        WHERE
            U.USER_ID = B.WRITER_USER_ID) AS "userNickNm",
        (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_BOARD_LIKE L 
        WHERE
            L.CN_BOARD_NO = B.CN_BOARD_NO) AS "boardLikeCnt",
        (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_BOARD_DETAIL D 
        WHERE
            D.CN_BOARD_NO = B.CN_BOARD_NO 
            AND D.REPLY_STAT_CD = 'A') AS "boardReplyCnt" 
    FROM
        CN_BOARD_TYPE K 
    INNER JOIN
        CN_BOARD B 
            ON B.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO = K.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO 
    WHERE
        K.CN_NO = ?   
        AND K.BOARD_TYPE_STAT_CD = 'A'   
        AND B.BOARD_STAT_CD = 'A'   
        AND B.INS_DTIME >= TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '31 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000' 
    ORDER BY
        "boardLikeCnt" DESC 
    LIMIT
        3

        K.CN_NO = ?   
        AND K.BOARD_TYPE_STAT_CD = 'A'   
        AND B.BOARD_STAT_CD = 'A'   
        AND B.INS_DTIME >= TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '31 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000' 
    ORDER BY
        "boardLikeCnt" DESC 
    LIMIT
        3

2026-02-07T20:26:33.986+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-7] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        K.CN_NO AS "cnNo",
        K.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO AS "cnBoardTypeNo",
        B.CN_BOARD_NO AS "cnBoardNo",
        B.TITLE AS "title",
        B.INS_DTIME AS "regDate",
        (SELECT
            U.USER_NICK_NM 
        FROM
            MM_USER U 
        WHERE
            U.USER_ID = B.WRITER_USER_ID) AS "userNickNm",
        (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_BOARD_LIKE L 
        WHERE
            L.CN_BOARD_NO = B.CN_BOARD_NO) AS "boardLikeCnt",
        (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_BOARD_DETAIL D 
        WHERE
            D.CN_BOARD_NO = B.CN_BOARD_NO 
            AND D.REPLY_STAT_CD = 'A') AS "boardReplyCnt" 
    FROM
        CN_BOARD_TYPE K 
    INNER JOIN
        CN_BOARD B 
            ON B.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO = K.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO 
    WHERE
        K.CN_NO = ?   
        AND K.BOARD_TYPE_STAT_CD = 'A'   
        AND B.BOARD_STAT_CD = 'A'   
        AND B.INS_DTIME >= TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '31 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000' 
    ORDER BY
        "boardLikeCnt" DESC 
    LIMIT
        3
Hibernate: 
    SELECT
        K.CN_NO AS "cnNo",
        K.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO AS "cnBoardTypeNo",

        B.TITLE AS "title",
        B.INS_DTIME AS "regDate",
        (SELECT
            U.USER_NICK_NM 
        FROM
            MM_USER U 
        WHERE
            U.USER_ID = B.WRITER_USER_ID) AS "userNickNm",
        (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_BOARD_LIKE L 
        WHERE
            L.CN_BOARD_NO = B.CN_BOARD_NO) AS "boardLikeCnt",
        (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_BOARD_DETAIL D 
        WHERE
            D.CN_BOARD_NO = B.CN_BOARD_NO 
            AND D.REPLY_STAT_CD = 'A') AS "boardReplyCnt" 
    FROM
        CN_BOARD_TYPE K 
    INNER JOIN
        CN_BOARD B 
            ON B.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO = K.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO 
    WHERE
        K.CN_NO = ?

2026-02-07T20:27:05.347+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-2] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        K.CN_NO AS "cnNo",
        K.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO AS "cnBoardTypeNo",
        B.CN_BOARD_NO AS "cnBoardNo",
        B.TITLE AS "title",
        B.INS_DTIME AS "regDate",
        (SELECT
            U.USER_NICK_NM 
        FROM
            MM_USER U 
        WHERE
            U.USER_ID = B.WRITER_USER_ID) AS "userNickNm",
        (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_BOARD_LIKE L 
        WHERE
            L.CN_BOARD_NO = B.CN_BOARD_NO) AS "boardLikeCnt",
        (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_BOARD_DETAIL D 
        WHERE
            D.CN_BOARD_NO = B.CN_BOARD_NO 
            AND D.REPLY_STAT_CD = 'A') AS "boardReplyCnt" 
    FROM
        CN_BOARD_TYPE K 
    INNER JOIN
        CN_BOARD B 
            ON B.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO = K.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO 
    WHERE
        K.CN_NO = ?   
        AND K.BOARD_TYPE_STAT_CD = 'A'   
        AND B.BOARD_STAT_CD = 'A'   
        AND B.INS_DTIME >= TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '31 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000' 
    ORDER BY
        "boardLikeCnt" DESC 
    LIMIT
        3
Hibernate: 
    SELECT
        K.CN_NO AS "cnNo",
        K.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO AS "cnBoardTypeNo",
        B.CN_BOARD_NO AS "cnBoardNo",
        B.TITLE AS "title",
        B.INS_DTIME AS "regDate",
        (SELECT
            U.USER_NICK_NM 
        FROM
            MM_USER U 
        WHERE
            U.USER_ID = B.WRITER_USER_ID) AS "userNickNm",
        (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_BOARD_LIKE L 
        WHERE
            L.CN_BOARD_NO = B.CN_BOARD_NO) AS "boardLikeCnt",
        (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_BOARD_DETAIL D 
        WHERE
            D.CN_BOARD_NO = B.CN_BOARD_NO 
            AND D.REPLY_STAT_CD = 'A') AS "boardReplyCnt" 
    FROM
        CN_BOARD_TYPE K 
    INNER JOIN
        CN_BOARD B 
            ON B.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO = K.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO 
    WHERE
        K.CN_NO = ?   
        AND K.BOARD_TYPE_STAT_CD = 'A'   
        AND B.BOARD_STAT_CD = 'A'   
        AND B.INS_DTIME >= TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '31 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000' 
    ORDER BY
        "boardLikeCnt" DESC 
    LIMIT
        3

            count(ccm1_0.cn_msg_no) 
        from
            cn_chat_message ccm1_0 
        where
            ccm1_0.cn_no=cg1_0.cn_no 
            and ccm1_0.snd_user_id<>?

                ccmr1_0.cn_msg_no, ccmr1_0.read_user_id from cn_chat_message_read ccmr1_0

2026-02-07T20:27:05.358+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-5] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        K.CN_NO AS "cnNo",
        K.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO AS "cnBoardTypeNo",
        B.CN_BOARD_NO AS "cnBoardNo",
        B.TITLE AS "title",
        B.INS_DTIME AS "regDate",
        (SELECT
            U.USER_NICK_NM 
        FROM
            MM_USER U 
        WHERE
            U.USER_ID = B.WRITER_USER_ID) AS "userNickNm",
        (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_BOARD_LIKE L 
        WHERE
            L.CN_BOARD_NO = B.CN_BOARD_NO) AS "boardLikeCnt",
        (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_BOARD_DETAIL D 
        WHERE
            D.CN_BOARD_NO = B.CN_BOARD_NO 
            AND D.REPLY_STAT_CD = 'A') AS "boardReplyCnt" 
    FROM
        CN_BOARD_TYPE K 
    INNER JOIN
        CN_BOARD B 
            ON B.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO = K.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO 
    WHERE
        K.CN_NO = ?   
        AND K.BOARD_TYPE_STAT_CD = 'A'   
        AND B.BOARD_STAT_CD = 'A'   
        AND B.INS_DTIME >= TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '31 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000' 
    ORDER BY
        "boardLikeCnt" DESC 
    LIMIT
        3

        (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_BOARD_LIKE L 
        WHERE
            L.CN_BOARD_NO = B.CN_BOARD_NO) AS "boardLikeCnt",
        (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_BOARD_DETAIL D 
        WHERE
            D.CN_BOARD_NO = B.CN_BOARD_NO 
            AND D.REPLY_STAT_CD = 'A') AS "boardReplyCnt" 
    FROM
        CN_BOARD_TYPE K

        CN_BOARD B 
            ON B.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO = K.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO

        "boardLikeCnt" DESC 
    LIMIT
        3
Hibernate: 
    SELECT
        K.CN_NO AS "cnNo",
        K.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO AS "cnBoardTypeNo",
        B.CN_BOARD_NO AS "cnBoardNo",
        B.TITLE AS "title",
        B.INS_DTIME AS "regDate",
        (SELECT
            U.USER_NICK_NM 
        FROM
            MM_USER U 
        WHERE
            U.USER_ID = B.WRITER_USER_ID) AS "userNickNm",
        (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_BOARD_LIKE L 
        WHERE
            L.CN_BOARD_NO = B.CN_BOARD_NO) AS "boardLikeCnt",
        (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_BOARD_DETAIL D 
        WHERE
            D.CN_BOARD_NO = B.CN_BOARD_NO 
            AND D.REPLY_STAT_CD = 'A') AS "boardReplyCnt" 
    FROM
        CN_BOARD_TYPE K 
    INNER JOIN
        CN_BOARD B 
            ON B.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO = K.CN_BOARD_TYPE_NO 
    WHERE
        K.CN_NO = ?   
        AND K.BOARD_TYPE_STAT_CD = 'A'   
        AND B.BOARD_STAT_CD = 'A'   
        AND B.INS_DTIME >= TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '31 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000' 
    ORDER BY
        "boardLikeCnt" DESC 
    LIMIT
        3

    SELECT
        CNR.CN_NO        AS ROOM_NO,
        -- 클랜채팅방번호
         CNR.CN_ROOM_NM   AS ROOM_NM,
        -- 클랜채팅방이름
         (           SELECT
            MSG.MSG           
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.CN_NO = CNR.CN_NO             
            AND MSG.SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'           
        ORDER BY
            MSG.SND_DTIME DESC           
        LIMIT
            1         ) AS NEW_MSG,
        -- 신규메시지
         (           SELECT
            COUNT(1)           
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.CN_NO = CNR.CN_NO             
            AND MSG.SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                   AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'             
            AND NOT EXISTS (                 SELECT
                1                 FROM CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ MSR                 
            WHERE
                MSR.CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO                   
                AND MSR.READ_USER_ID = ?             )         ) AS NEW_MSG_READ_CNT,
        -- 채팅읽지않은건수
         'CLAN' AS ROOM_TYPE,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH     
    FROM
        CN_USER CNU     
    INNER JOIN
        CN_GROUP CNG 
            ON CNG.CN_NO = CNU.CN_NO     
    INNER JOIN
        CN_CHAT_ROOM CNR 
            ON CNR.CN_NO = CNU.CN_NO     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = CNG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        CNU.CN_USER_ID = ?         
        AND CNU.CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A'         
        AND CNU.CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN'         
        AND CNG.CN_STAT_CD = 'A'         
        AND CNG.CN_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN'      
    UNION
    ALL      SELECT
        CNR.BN_NO        AS ROOM_NO,
        -- 합주채팅방번호
         CNR.BN_ROOM_NM   AS ROOM_NM,

        FROM

        WHERE

            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'           
        ORDER BY
            MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME DESC           
        LIMIT
            1         ) AS NEW_MSG,
        -- 신규메시지
         (           SELECT
            COUNT(1)           
        FROM
            BN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG           
        WHERE
            MSG.BN_NO = CNR.BN_NO             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_USER_ID <> ?             
            AND MSG.BN_CHAT_SND_DTIME BETWEEN TO_CHAR(NOW() - INTERVAL '30 days', 'YYYYMMDD') || '000000'                                           AND TO_CHAR(NOW(), 'YYYYMMDD') || '999999'

            WHERE

                AND MSR.BN_CHAT_READ_USER_ID = ?             )         ) AS NEW_MSG_READ_CNT,
        -- 채팅읽지않은건수
         'BAND' AS ROOM_TYPE,
        NULL AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH

2026-02-07T20:27:50.616+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-1] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30 
Hibernate: 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

2026-02-07T20:28:14.755+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-2] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

2026-02-07T20:28:14.770+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-9] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,

    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30 
Hibernate: 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

2026-02-07T20:28:54.821+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-6] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,

        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT

        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC

        30

2026-02-07T20:29:15.837+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-3] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE

        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID

        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO

2026-02-07T20:29:15.852+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [nio-8083-exec-1] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30

2026-02-07T20:30:38.050+09:00 DEBUG 18076 --- [bandi-backend] [io-8083-exec-10] org.hibernate.SQL                        : 
    SELECT
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO,
        MSG.CN_NO,
        MSG.SND_USER_ID,
        USR.USER_NICK_NM,
        MSG.MSG,
        MSG.MSG_TYPE_CD,
        MSG.SND_DTIME,
        NULL AS PROFILE_URL,
        (           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_USER 
        WHERE
            CN_NO = MSG.CN_NO 
            AND CN_USER_STAT_CD = 'A' 
            AND CN_USER_APPR_STAT_CD = 'CN')           -           (SELECT
            COUNT(1) 
        FROM
            CN_CHAT_MESSAGE_READ 
        WHERE
            CN_MSG_NO = MSG.CN_MSG_NO)         ) AS UNREAD_CNT,
        MSG.ATTACH_NO,
        CMA.FILE_PATH AS ATTACH_FILE_PATH,
        CMA.FILE_NAME AS ATTACH_FILE_NM,
        MSG.VOTE_NO     
    FROM
        CN_CHAT_MESSAGE MSG     
    LEFT JOIN
        MM_USER USR 
            ON USR.USER_ID = MSG.SND_USER_ID     
    LEFT JOIN
        CM_ATTACHMENT CMA 
            ON CMA.ATTACH_NO = MSG.ATTACH_NO     
    WHERE
        MSG.CN_NO = ?     
        AND MSG.CHAT_STAT_CD = 'A'  
    ORDER BY
        MSG.CN_MSG_NO DESC 
    LIMIT
        30
